helpTopic.p:
CX generates the Device Configuration Descriptor for the node.  It also generates the Software Component and Software Package Descriptors 
			for each device or Core Framework entity contained in the node.  If you have defined properties for the devices or Core Framework entities, 
			CX generates the Property Descriptors, as well.

